-03T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n覺得去到紅隧果吓已經算今日任務完成<br />\n後面就有少少做多咗<br />\n起碼唔好玩到咁夜"},{"pid":"b64829acf1aed35d8af87d28b0e04698fc08bdb4","tid":1400931,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1693413d06eca7168cff977afbc4d8c1ff809a84","tid":1400931,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387ec50bad41dda4db37e5e28e453675c3d9652f","tid":1400931,"uid":51271,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"e4dd892e324c1e0f96a3ad22568660c49f7fff8a","tid":1400931,"uid":34065,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"鬼你老母 義士企到最前 被拉告暴動<br />\n最多都係諗法唔同 鬼乜撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"我真係唔識講，你話七月頭唔識散我無野好講，元朗同西環一戰後好明顯要走得快。<br />\n<br />\n我見紅隧大家走得咁醒目，諗住大家終於識醒，點知又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"多撚餘你可以話佢地戀戰 送頭 <br />\n但鬼真係好撚ON鳩<br />\n又變返捉鬼捉鬼<br />\n5年前就係捉鬼捉撚到散哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單就係蠢<br />\n仲唔承認錯誤 我勸佢哋唔好做前線"},{"pid":"99a7913be9d3aad671cf3d2d8a891e397630b9dd","tid":1400931,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517f49a29d9b94f0a12313ebfdb0a78fc69a1d4d","tid":1400931,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65bc02d65a65272722e18a538a5945746262ac9b","tid":1400931,"uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"13c1e16fce7e8d3db59de9b3b7f7d754a6272a70","tid":1400931,"uid":44358,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽講句，一定有鬼。<br />\n<br />\n只有快閃式 (馬鞍山、天水圍)，黑警安排唔切內應，義士先可以全身而退。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"葵涌、馬鞍山、天水圍全部都係走人唔落單，但點解一到周末就傻晒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"weekday都出個D係老鬼, 周末個D有D新兵, 於是唔識走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"其實調轉"},{"pid":"7532a832261cac19a1a22d17767be0